{
  "stem": "13524.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow he must have been notified by-- from the Jewish headquarters-- from the office where the policeman were-- probably about people like [INAUDIBLE] and Dr.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Greenberg, who was also in that group of 100.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know who else was that was family or somebody that they wanted to save.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sent for Schindler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Come and save that 100 because they're all going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Schindler realized and used that excuse-- the women-- to get Amon Goeth down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Amon Goeth went down, and we were not shot that day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Today I realized that it was Schindler, not-- knowing then who Schindler was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I knew about Emalia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I knew that there was a working place in Zablocie, out of ghetto, that if you had certain amount of money you could get in and you could work and be saved.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow we never had sufficient money to get in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we felt secure in the house where we lived because we had somebody there who would tell us when there is transport to go.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It sort of gave a certain sense of false security.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because if the SS would have walked into that house, we would have been finished, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How does a girl of 16 cope with been whipped publicly like that?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very humiliating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dehumanizing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For life-- not because the SS have seen my bottom, but because of the rest of the Jews, the people who stood there, amongst them there were young boys whom I knew from before.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to be hit, to take off the knickers and to be whipped on bare bottom-- it was a hell of a lot to live with after.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, that wasn't the first time in the last time.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
